title: Gaggenau Refrigerator Door Gasket - White
description: Gaggenau Refrigerator Door Gasket - White ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 22 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11759516 Manufacturer Part Number W10830189 The door gasket is used to make an air-tight seal for the cabinet when the door is closed.

installationInstructions.author: Frederic from KILLEEN, TX
installationInstructions.title: Right door seal lower tab was torn.
installationInstructions.content: Unpacked, inspected, found two minor defects in the form of two tiny slivers along the seal edge which I cut with a small scissor, laid the seal down on the kitchen table, applied heat to the deformed areas and reshaped them with my fingers, heated the entire seal lightly, removed the old seal starting at the right hand upper corner using my fingers, installed the warm seal starting at the top corners by pushing it in its slot making sure the outer lip stayed out of the slot and worked my way around. I believe that the heat from the dryer made it pliable and easier to manage.
